For first release
=================
* Type conversion tests, lots of them, create databases with various sql types
  and make sure thet get converted correctly to ruby classes
* Tests on transactions
* amalgalite command line tool

For future releases
===================

* Blob interface
* authorizers
* busy timeouts
* progress handler
* loading of extensions
* utf-16 integration
* create_collation 
* global temp directory
* create_function
* full text search
* virtual file system
* encryption key support
